slidelink.displaytext: 1. As per the given case study, identify the person/s who are demonstrating active citizenship in alignment with constitutional values. Residents of ABC group housing society are having an emergency meeting after one of the residents in the society have tested positive for COVID 19. Listen to the conversation among the residents and identify who all are demonstrating constitutional values that will help build a civil society in these testing times. Based on your learning from this module, select all the options that you think are appropriate.
